Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我還是應該把這報告書公佈於世嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好不好
