Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對  就是這樣  感覺不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼接下來試試那一招吧
